high_descs: Turn left and head straight to the wall, Hang right, then make a left into the kitchen and turn right towards the countertop.
Pick up the onion from the countertop.
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the sink.
Place the onion in the sink and fill the sink with water, Wash it, then pick up the onion.
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn right towards the fridge.
Keep the onion inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Washing the onion and storing it in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk out of the bedroom, turn left and enter the kitchen stopping by the far countertop.
Pick up the onion from the counter.
Place the onion in the sink, wash it off, and pick it back up.
Open the fridge and place the onion on the lowest shelf inside then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed off onion into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the counter top.
Take the onion from the counter top.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the onion into the sink and washed it.
Then take it out and go near the fridge.
Put the onion into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Placed the onion into the fridge.
